            <title>[PDFBOX-3615] Multiply transparency not anti-aliased</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3615</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Not sure if this is related to other transparency issues like &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3000&quot; title=&quot;Transparency Group issues&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3000&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3000&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but I noticed that certain elements were really jagged in my PDFs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It looks like items with multiply transparency applied aren&apos;t anti-aliased.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve attached an example PDF and resulting PNG from pdfbox-app-2.0.3.jar&lt;/p&gt;</description>
